</li>\r\n 	<li>Provide training on report generation and data use</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nSee you there.\r\n\r\n<strong>Agenda:</strong>\r\n<a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/emr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/National-OpenMRS-ToT-Agenda-Final-2016.pdf\">national-openmrs-tot-agenda-final-2016</a>','National OpenMRS ToT','','publish','closed','closed','','national-openmrs-tot','','','2016-11-10 06:22:33','2016-11-10 06:22:33','',0,'http://127.0.0.1/emr/?post_type=event&#038;p=5347',0,'event','',0),(5348,1,'2016-11-10 06:22:20','2016-11-10 06:22:20','','national-openmrs-tot-agenda-final-2016','','inherit','open','closed','','national-openmrs-tot-agenda-final-2016','','','2016-11-10 06:22:20','2016-11-10 06:22:20','',5347,'http://127.0.0.1/emr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/National-OpenMRS-ToT-Agenda-Final-2016.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(5350,1,'2016-11-10 06:31:49','2016-11-10 06:31:49','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vestibulum eu elit nibh. Nunc ac leo viverra, efficitur libero et, rhoncus eros. In et volutpat libero. Fusce purus justo, cursus ut ante ac, iaculis sagittis mauris. Nam sollicitudin ultricies faucibus. Vestibulum vehicula fringilla purus quis varius. Nunc aliquet nisl non elit condimentum, eu rutrum justo placerat. Fusce et nulla placerat, scelerisque ex a, maximus dolor. Proin rhoncus nisl quis eleifend ultricies. Curabitur sem mauris, interdum quis elementum ac, pharetra congue lectus. Nam non ipsum a quam molestie convallis. Curabitur ultrices sed sapien hendrerit bibendum. Suspendisse vestibulum quam ac arcu vestibulum, placerat feugiat mi commodo. Morbi tortor ante, mollis non libero sed, luctus egestas ex. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Mauris vitae viverra mi.','OpenMRS implementer\'s conference','','publish','closed','closed','','openmrs-implementers-conference','','','2016-11-10 06:35:20','2016-11-10 06:35:20','',0,'http://127.0.0.1/emr/?post_type=event&#038;p=5350',0,'event','',0),(5351,1,'2016-11-10 06:31:49','2016-11-10 06:31:49','','Serena kampala hotel','','publish','open','closed','','serena-kampala-hotel','','','2016-11-10 06:31:49','2016-11-10 06:31:49','',0,'http://127.0.0.1/emr/locations/serena-kampala-hotel/',0,'location','',0),(5353,1,'2016-11-14 18:17:43','2016-11-14 18:17:43','<h2 class=\"title\">Supported by</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\" alt=\"Logo 1\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/emr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/cdc1.png\">\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\" alt=\"Logo 2\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/emr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/moh-2.png\">\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\" alt=\"Logo 3\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/emr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/who1.png\">\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\" alt=\"Logo 3\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/emr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/pepfar.png\">\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\" alt=\"Logo 3\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/emr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ucsf1.png\">\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\" alt=\"Logo 3\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/emr/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/muk.png\">\r\n<h3 class=\"fancy-header\">EMR Project FAQ\'s</h3>\r\n<h4>Who is UgandaEMR for?</h4>\r\n<p>UgandaEMR is for people that need to implement a medical records system. It is both just a library of API calls and a database and a default implementation of those API calls in the form of a web application.</p>\r\n<h4>What is UgandaEMR?</h4>\r\n<p>UgandaEMR is an application which enables design of a customized medical records system with no programming knowledge (although medical and systems analysis knowledge is required). </p>\r\n<h4>Where is UgandaEMR being used?</h4>\r\n<p>UgandaERM is in about 340 sites across Uganda. Further implementations are underway in other locations locally. Nearly five hundred thousand discrete observa